    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/7b1bfcd9b28f6a4ee9b642cc4f41f78a.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=540 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/7b1bfcd9b28f6a4ee9b642cc4f41f78a.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/7b1bfcd9b28f6a4ee9b642cc4f41f78a.mp4?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>DEMO LIMITATIONS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Soul Kira Demo provides access to only Solo / Free For All mode and none of the Team game modes.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Soul Kira Demo provides access only to a limited number of maps and none of the Large Scale Team Battle Maps.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Soul Kira Demo's Character Creator system has limited number of body parts available. Although, the Unique body part combination enforcement works same for both Demo and Full Game</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Game/Demo is still being actively developed and updated 2-3 times each week. Please follow progress and leave feedback through our discord or Steam Discussions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >---------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soul Kira is a multiplayer 2D Platform Shooter game, taking gameplay elements from Shoot 'em Up, Dungeon Crawler and Roguelike. Soul Kira currently supports upto 16 players in a match, with plans to scale upto 100 players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Modes:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-PvP Mode: Free for All, fight against other players in solo battles or as a team</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-PvE Mode: Fight monsters and other entities in the Soul Kira universe, clear dungeons and levels like a retro arcade game and unlock rewards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-PvPvE Mode: Total chaos ensues when players will have to fight other players and also monsters in a free for all. Beware of other Monarch Bosses also taking part in battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapons Available (Both in Demo and Full Game):</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Pistol <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/4d66dcbbe7b00badc50f38a70ff40748.webp?t=1728925234\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/4d66dcbbe7b00badc50f38a70ff40748.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" class=\"bb_img\" width=114 height=64 /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Rifle <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/9508dae98f8ce080f52676e46c7cd929.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/9508dae98f8ce080f52676e46c7cd929.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Machine Gun <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/6a0ea4beadde263e2ebd01a4e7899562.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/6a0ea4beadde263e2ebd01a4e7899562.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > SMG <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/45280716d6a3b1a6197784d8716438cc.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/45280716d6a3b1a6197784d8716438cc.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shotgun <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/9d2f810c1d1224c9b035b53b591ff74c.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/9d2f810c1d1224c9b035b53b591ff74c.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sniper <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/831cd598f9f7f2c83b7caa8c0ad34b58.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/831cd598f9f7f2c83b7caa8c0ad34b58.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Bazooka <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/ccaa4777ef6845e94351b748ce61b01b.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/ccaa4777ef6845e94351b748ce61b01b.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Flamethrower<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/83932f40666ecb55fe300dfca7bbe592.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/83932f40666ecb55fe300dfca7bbe592.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grenade <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/d2359ffd3c8f6a24ee845e760eef9f99.webp?t=1728925234\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/d2359ffd3c8f6a24ee845e760eef9f99.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" class=\"bb_img\" width=114 height=64 /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Frag Grenade <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/2d878ce5a9ea15fbf2fbab508bff7bb2.webp?t=1728925234\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/2d878ce5a9ea15fbf2fbab508bff7bb2.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" class=\"bb_img\" width=114 height=64 /></picture></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Toxic Grenade <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/267b2610bc18e9eb8653fd90be6a8c3e.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=114 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/267b2610bc18e9eb8653fd90be6a8c3e.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >----------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Creator System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Character Creator System allows each player to create their own Unique Character by customizing different body parts and cosmetics of their character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>In Soul Kira Demo, The Character Creator System Features Limited Body Part options compared to the full game.</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/4831d3c8494768a6722798bd25eb3c0f.poster.avif?t=1728925234\" width=800 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/4831d3c8494768a6722798bd25eb3c0f.webm?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184070/extras/4831d3c8494768a6722798bd25eb3c0f.mp4?t=1728925234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Character Creator enforces that there can only exist one unique character of a type, which means no same character with combination of body parts/cosmetics used can be created again, making sure each and every character in Soul Kira will always be unique (looking).</p>",
